 of beer styles to the table and strive for perfection, so you’re sure to find a tasty brew that matches your palate! So, raise a brew with us all month long and take home great swag every Thursday after 5!\nLearn More\nPint night Every Thursday\nSolid Gold\nLager\nMosaic Promise\nPale Ale\nCentennial\nIPA\nDirty Bastard\nScotch Ale\nJoin our\nbrewniversity!\nEarn your beer drinking degree and rake in the rewards. Our Brewniversity program is the perfect way to try tons of new brews and earn some great prizes from bigger pours at the bar to trips around the world. Join now and get started on your degree!\njoin brewniversity\nThe Southeast's\nNeighborhood Bar\nAbout Taco Mac\nSince 1979, our world-class wings, curated craft beer menus, and love for our home teams have set the scene for friends and family to gather and celebrate moments of all sizes. We offer an experience focused on quality, driven by outstanding service, and supported by those who are proud to call Taco Mac their home bar.\nlearn more\nClosest Location\nSwitch Location\nConyers\nMacon\nPelham\nDawsonville\nGainesville\nHiram\nLawrenceville\nSuwanee\nPeachtree City\nNewnan\nMarietta\nKennesaw\nJohns Creek\nDuluth\nDouglasville\nCumming\nCumberland\nCrabapple\nCanton\nOld Milton\nPrado\nWindward\nWoodstock\nMall of Georgia\nPerimeter\nMcDonough\nOrder Online\nView Menu\nJoin E-Club\nMiles Away!\nMore details\nOn Tap:\n\n--- Page: /wp-content/uploads/2026/01/608-x-1080-Every-hour-is-Happy-hour-v.jpg ---\n����\u0000\u0018Exif\u0000\u0000II*\u0000\b\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0000��\u0000\u0011Ducky\u0000\u0001\u0000\u0004\u0000\u0000\u0000d\u0000\u0000��\u0003�http://ns.adobe.com/xap/1.0/\u0000\n��\u0000\u000eAdobe\u0000d�\u0000\u0000\u0000\u0001��\u0000�\u0000\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0001\u0